captions.text:
-(Orange) Check out my
brand-new Minecraft server,

-Hey,
I got a special delivery here.

ordered this here
pile of explosives.
I'm looking for one Mr. Orange.

-Orange? Why did you order
a pile of explosives?

-I prefer to ask,
why wouldn't I? [laughs]

-Dude, this is an
Ask Orange episode.

You know very well that
these are going to explode in--

-(announcer) "Hey Orange, Flappy
Bird's back in the kitchen!"

It's my first time operating
one of these things,
so give me a second to, um...

Oh, I forgot I had it
set to Taco Bell. [laughs]

Hey! That one might
be worth something!

-(announcer) "Look out!
Someone's going to lick you!"

Hey, get outta here, licorice.
Get outta here.

-But I love licking things.
Come on!

-(announcer) "Can you please put
chili sauce in someone's eyes?"

-Sure! Huh. Doesn't seem
to be anybody around.

Guess I'll just put it
in my own eye--

[screaming]: Why?!
Why would I do this to myself!

-(announcer) "Do you love
Passion Fruit? A clean answer!"

-All right, all right.
I'll give you a clean answer.

-I came as soon as I heard.
-As did I, Robinero Sauce.

Just singin' the theme song,
that's all.

-(announcer) "Have you ever
had a near death moment?"

but if I ever do have a scrape
with death, perhaps I'll--

I kinda feel like a lot of that
stuff hasn't even happened yet.

-(announcer) "Please tell me if
Marshmallow is a boy or girl.

Does Midget Apple
have a SMALL chance?"

-Here comes the pain,
Marshmallow! Get ready!

-[grunting] Um,
this sword is kinda of heavy.

-Ah, come on,
don't say that right now.

-I love fights! Almost as
much as I love you! YAY!!!

and "How long can you
burp after drinking Zoop?"

-All right, we're about
to find out the answer

to both of those questions
right now.
Ready with the radar gun, Pear?

But honestly, I don't even know
why I bother anymore.

-I think I'm gonna need
a bigger radar gun.

-Special delivery! I've got this
second pile of explosives here.
